---
title: Steak and Cauliflower Rice with parsley butter and veg
description: Cauliflower rice is lower in calories and higher in fibre than regular rice, making it a great substitute for those looking to make healthy changes in their diet. It's also the perfect understated pairing for the rich steak and moreish veg in this recipe.
